> do a similar check (*) and to also add special backlight drivers like
> nvidia-wmi-ec-backlight and drivers/video/backlight/apple_bl.c
> to this mechanism.


nvidia-wmi-ec-backlight does this check during probe:

> Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  ret = wmi_brightness_notify(wdev, WMI_BRIGHTNESS_METHOD_SOURCE,
> Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  WMI_BRIGHTNESS_MODE_GET, &source);
> Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  if (ret)
